  "description": "<i>?ycie Maklera</i> is a text based economic game. As a mine owner the player must keep as long as possible owned assets. The player may trade mines, sell ore and pay miners wages. Each mine requires ten employed miners. Miners payment affects the level of life and therefore the size of ore extraction. Every year the price of mine, ore and food is changing. Proper use of price trends is the key to wealth multiplication.<br><br><i>?ycie Maklera</i> is an unofficial port of C64/ZX Spectrum's game of the same title.",
